  <brief_title>Study to Look at the Effects of ART-123 on Patients With Sepsis and Disseminated Intravascular Coagulation (DIC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Phase 2B Study ot Assess the Safety and Efficacy Effects of ART-123 on Subjects With Sepsis and Disseminated Intravascular Coagulation</official_title>
