  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Bacterial or suspected bacterial infection

          2. Presents with 2 or more sepsis related SIRS criteria within 24hours prior to any
             particular qualifying DIC score.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnant

          2. Unwilling to allow transfusion of blood or blood products

          3. Body weight&gt; or equal to 175kg.
      </textblock>
